---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Services">
	<section class="bg-blue-900 text-white py-24 flex items-center justify-center">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-6 text-center">
			<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold mb-4 tracking-tight drop-shadow-lg">Tailored Business Solutions</h1>
			<p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-blue-100 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed font-light italic">
				We help you stop worrying about spreadsheets and start focusing on growth. 
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-24 bg-white">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-6">
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center mb-24">
				<div class="order-2 md:order-1">
					<div class="w-20 h-20 bg-blue-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-10 text-blue-600 shadow-sm border border-blue-50">
						<svg class="w-10 h-10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path></svg>
					</div>
					<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900 leading-tight">Expert Bookkeeping</h2>
					<p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-lg mb-8 font-light italic">
						Precision financial tracking is the foundation of every successful business. 
						Hidden Hills LLC provides thorough bookkeeping services so you always have a clear view of your financial health.
					</p>
					<ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-700 font-medium">
						<li class="flex items-center space-x-4"><span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-600 rounded-full"></span><span>Accurate accounts receivable & payable</span></li>
						<li class="flex items-center space-x-4"><span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-600 rounded-full"></span><span>Monthly bank and credit card reconciliations</span></li>
						<li class="flex items-center space-x-4"><span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-600 rounded-full"></span><span>Comprehensive financial reporting & insights</span></li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="order-1 md:order-2 bg-gray-50 p-12 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
					<div class="text-center italic text-gray-400 text-lg py-12">"Focus on your craft. Let us handle the numbers."</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center mb-24">
				<div class="bg-gray-50 p-12 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
					<div class="text-center italic text-gray-400 text-lg py-12">"Efficiency is the difference between surviving and thriving."</div>
				</div>
				<div>
					<div class="w-20 h-20 bg-blue-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-10 text-blue-600 shadow-sm border border-blue-50">
						<svg class="w-10 h-10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg>
					</div>
					<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900 leading-tight">Financial Process Improvement</h2>
					<p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-lg mb-8 font-light italic">
						Is your business held back by outdated workflows? We specialize in identifying friction and implementing 
						efficient, modern financial processes that save time and reduce errors.
					</p>
					<ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-700 font-medium">
						<li class="flex items-center space-x-4"><span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-600 rounded-full"></span><span>Workflow audits and optimization</span></li>
						<li class="flex items-center space-x-4"><span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-600 rounded-full"></span><span>Tech stack integration & automation</span></li>
						<li class="flex items-center space-x-4"><span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-600 rounded-full"></span><span>Internal control development</span></li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
				<div>
					<div class="w-20 h-20 bg-blue-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-10 text-blue-600 shadow-sm border border-blue-50">
						<svg class="w-10 h-10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 17V7m0 10a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V7a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m0 10a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 7a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m0 10V7m0 10a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2a2 2 0 00-2 2"></path></svg>
					</div>
					<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900 leading-tight">Spreadsheet Creation & Consulting</h2>
					<p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-lg mb-8 font-light italic">
						We create powerful, custom spreadsheet tools tailored specifically to your data needs. 
						From budgeting templates to complex project trackers, we build systems that work for you.
					</p>
					<ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-700 font-medium">
						<li class="flex items-center space-x-4"><span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-600 rounded-full"></span><span>Custom budgeting & forecasting tools</span></li>
						<li class="flex items-center space-x-4"><span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-600 rounded-full"></span><span>Dashboard creation & data visualization</span></li>
						<li class="flex items-center space-x-4"><span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-600 rounded-full"></span><span>Strategic business consulting sessions</span></li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="bg-gray-50 p-12 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
					<div class="text-center italic text-gray-400 text-lg py-12">"Data-driven decisions for long-term success."</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
